## Technical Specifications

### Requirements Analysis

1. Core Platform Infrastructure
   - Decentralized storage system using IPFS
   - Smart contracts for access control and ownership
   - AI processing pipeline for content enhancement
   - React-based frontend with Web3 integration

2. AI Components
   - Natural Language Processing for narrative generation
   - Computer Vision for photo analysis and enhancement
   - Audio processing for voice memories
   - Machine Learning for personalization

3. Blockchain Integration
   - NFT-based ownership system
   - Decentralized identity management
   - Smart contract-based access control
   - Token economics for storage incentives

4. User Experience
   - Intuitive content upload interface
   - Interactive memory visualization
   - Social sharing features
   - Mobile-first design

### Requirements Pool

P0 (Must-have):
- Secure user authentication and wallet integration
- Basic memory upload (photos, text, audio)
- IPFS storage integration
- AI-powered memory enhancement
- Basic sharing capabilities
- Mobile-responsive interface

P1 (Should-have):
- Multiple AI narrative styles
- Advanced privacy controls
- Memory tagging and categorization
- Interactive 3D memory scenes
- Collaborative memory spaces
- Token-based incentive system

P2 (Nice-to-have):
- AR/VR memory visualization
- Sensory data integration
- AI-powered memory suggestions
- Cross-platform synchronization
- Advanced analytics dashboard
- Memory time-capsule scheduling

